The paper deals with the application of hyperbolic geometry in machine learning, specifically in the context of neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves natural language processing tasks, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of neural networks also implies the possibility of it being categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves classification tasks, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
